{"id": "figure_004", "modality": "figures", "name": "Feature Pyramid Network (FPN)", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces a Feature Pyramid Network figure. Title 'Feature Pyramid Network (FPN)' at top in 32px bold. LEFT column: a bottom-up backbone pathway with FOUR feature-map boxes stacked vertically, drawn at DECREASING spatial size top-to-bottom toward higher levels, labelled 'C2 (1/4)', 'C3 (1/8)', 'C4 (1/16)', 'C5 (1/32)' with channel annotations. RIGHT column: a top-down pathway with FOUR corresponding output boxes 'P5', 'P4', 'P3', 'P2', each at the same vertical level as its backbone counterpart. For each level draw a horizontal '1x1 conv (lateral connection)' arrow from Ck to the merge point. From each higher Pk draw a '2x upsample' downward arrow that merges (element-wise '+' node) with the lateral connection to form the lower P-level. Each Pk is followed by a '3x3 conv' box producing the final pyramid feature. Annotate '256-d' on all P-level outputs. Four levels, four lateral connections, three upsample-merge arrows. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["All FOUR backbone boxes (C2-C5) and all FOUR pyramid boxes (P2-P5) plus their 3x3 conv boxes and merge nodes are visible with no clipping at any edge", "No two boxes overlap each other", "Every box label text (C2-C5, P2-P5, conv labels) is fully contained inside its box with no overflow", "Exactly FOUR lateral '1x1 conv' arrows connect each Ck to its corresponding Pk merge point, horizontally, without passing through other boxes", "Exactly THREE top-down '2x upsample' arrows connect each higher Pk down to the next merge node, and each terminates at a '+' merge node", "Each Ck box is horizontally aligned (same vertical level) with its corresponding Pk box", "Backbone boxes are drawn at decreasing spatial size from C2 (largest) to C5 (smallest), reflecting the pyramid", "The '256-d' channel annotation appears on the P-level outputs and is legible without colliding with other text", "Lateral arrows and upsample arrows do not overlap or cross through unrelated boxes", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 6157, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 6427}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 6891, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 6880}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 6179, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 5972}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_004_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_004_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Feature Pyramid Network (FPN)</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .content {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: flex-start;\n        }\n        \n        text {\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            text-anchor: middle;\n            dominant-baseline: central;\n        }\n        \n        .backbone-text {\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        \n        .pyramid-text {\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        \n        .conv-text {\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n            font-size: 12px;\n        }\n        \n        .channel-text {\n            fill: #7f8c8d;\n            font-size: 11px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-text {\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            text-anchor: start;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-title {\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-anchor: start;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title\">Feature Pyramid Network (FPN)</div>\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"980\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 980\">\n                <!-- Background -->\n                <rect width=\"1880\" height=\"980\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Backbone Pathway (Left Column) -->\n                <!-- C2 (largest, top) -->\n                <rect x=\"100\" y=\"100\" width=\"200\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"150\" class=\"backbone-text\">C2 (1/4)</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"170\" class=\"channel-text\">512 channels</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"190\" class=\"channel-text\">BxHxW</text>\n                \n                <!-- C3 -->\n                <rect x=\"120\" y=\"280\" width=\"160\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"320\" class=\"backbone-text\">C3 (1/8)</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"340\" class=\"channel-text\">1024 channels</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"360\" class=\"channel-text\">BxH/2xW/2</text>\n                \n                <!-- C4 -->\n                <rect x=\"140\" y=\"440\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"470\" class=\"backbone-text\">C4 (1/16)</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"490\" class=\"channel-text\">2048 channels</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"510\" class=\"channel-text\">BxH/4xW/4</text>\n                \n                <!-- C5 (smallest, bottom) -->\n                <rect x=\"160\" y=\"580\" width=\"80\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"605\" class=\"backbone-text\">C5 (1/32)</text>\n                <text x=\"200\" y=\"625\" class=\"channel-text\">2048 channels</text>\n                \n                <!-- Backbone arrows (bottom-up) -->\n                <path d=\"M 200 220 L 200 260\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 200 380 L 200 420\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 200 520 L 200 560\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Lateral Connections (1x1 conv) -->\n                <!-- C5 to P5 -->\n                <rect x=\"350\" y=\"595\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"410\" y=\"610\" class=\"conv-text\">1x1 conv</text>\n                <path d=\"M 240 610 L 330\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- C4 to merge point -->\n                <rect x=\"350\" y=\"465\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"410\" y=\"480\" class=\"conv-text\">1x1 conv</text>\n                <path d=\"M 260 480 L 330\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- C3 to merge point -->\n                <rect x=\"350\" y=\"315\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"410\" y=\"330\" class=\"conv-text\">1x1 conv</text>\n                <path d=\"M 280 330 L 330\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- C2 to merge point -->\n                <rect x=\"350\" y=\"145\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"410\" y=\"160\" class=\"conv-text\">1x1 conv</text>\n                <path d=\"M 300 160 L 330\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Upsample arrows (top-down) -->\n                <!-- P5 to P4 merge -->\n                <rect x=\"580\" y=\"540\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"630\" y=\"555\" class=\"conv-text\">2x upsample</text>\n                <path d=\"M 630 570 L 630 590 L 530 590 L 530 480\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- P4 to P3 merge -->\n                <rect x=\"580\" y=\"390\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"630\" y=\"405\" class=\"conv-text\">2x upsample</text>\n                <path d=\"M 630 420 L 630 440 L 530 440 L 530 330\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- P3 to P2 merge -->\n                <rect x=\"580\" y=\"240\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"630\" y=\"255\" class=\"conv-text\">2x upsample</text>\n                <path d=\"M 630 270 L 630 290 L 530 290 L 530 160\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Merge points (element-wise addition) -->\n                <circle cx=\"530\" cy=\"160\" r=\"15\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"530\" y=\"160\" class=\"conv-text\" fill=\"white\">+</text>\n                \n                <circle cx=\"530\" cy=\"330\" r=\"15\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"530\" y=\"330\" class=\"conv-text\" fill=\"white\">+</text>\n                \n                <circle cx=\"530\" cy=\"480\" r=\"15\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                <text x=\"530\" y=\"480\" class=\"conv-text\" fill=\"white\">+</text>\n                \n                <!-- Arrows from lateral connections to merge points -->\n                <path d=\"M 470 160 L 515 160\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 470 330 L 515 330\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 470 480 L 515 480\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Arrow from C5 lateral to P5 (no merge needed) -->\n                <path d=\"M 470 610 L 750 610\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- 3x3 Conv blocks -->\n                <rect x=\"750\" y=\"595\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"800\" y=\"610\" class=\"conv-text\">3x3 conv</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"750\" y=\"465\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"800\" y=\"480\" class=\"conv-text\">3x3 conv</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"750\" y=\"315\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"800\" y=\"330\" class=\"conv-text\">3x3 conv</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"750\" y=\"145\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                <text x=\"800\" y=\"160\" class=\"conv-text\">3x3 conv</text>\n                \n                <!-- Arrows from merge points to 3x3 conv -->\n                <path d=\"M 545 160 L 730\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 545 330 L 730\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 545 480 L 730\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Final Pyramid Features (Right Column) -->\n                <!-- P2 (largest, top) -->\n                <rect x=\"950\" y=\"100\" width=\"200\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#1abc9c\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"140\" class=\"pyramid-text\">P2</text>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"160\" class=\"channel-text\">256-d</text>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"180\" class=\"channel-text\">BxHxW</text>\n                \n                <!-- P3 -->\n                <rect x=\"970\" y=\"280\" width=\"160\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#1abc9c\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"320\" class=\"pyramid-text\">P3</text>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"340\" class=\"channel-text\">256-d</text>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"360\" class=\"channel-text\">BxH/2xW/2</text>\n                \n                <!-- P4 -->\n                <rect x=\"990\" y=\"440\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#1abc9c\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"470\" class=\"pyramid-text\">P4</text>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"490\" class=\"channel-text\">256-d</text>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"510\" class=\"channel-text\">BxH/4xW/4</text>\n                \n                <!-- P5 (smallest, bottom) -->\n                <rect x=\"1010\" y=\"580\" width=\"80\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#1abc9c\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"605\" class=\"pyramid-text\">P5</text>\n                <text x=\"1050\" y=\"625\" class=\"channel-text\">256-d</text>\n                \n                <!-- Arrows from 3x3 conv to final pyramid features -->\n                <path d=\"M 850 160 L 930\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 850 330 L 950\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 850 480 L 970\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n                <path d=\"M 850 610 L 990\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n                \n                <!-- Legend -->\n                <rect x=\"1300\" y=\"100\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n                <text x=\"1320\" y=\"130\" class=\"legend-title\">Legend</text>\n                \n                <!-- Legend items -->\n                <rect x=\"1320\" y=\"160\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                <text x=\"1360\" y=\"170\" class=\"legend-text\">Backbone Features (Ck)</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"1320\" y=\"190\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#1abc9c\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                <text x=\"1360\" y=\"200\" class=\"legend-text\">Pyramid Features (Pk)</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"1320\" y=\"220\" width=\"30\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                <text x=\"1360\" y=\"227\" class=\"legend-text\">1x1 Convolution</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"1320\" y=\"250\" width=\"30\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                <text x=\"1360\" y=\"257\" class=\"legend-text\">2x Upsample</text>\n                \n                <rect x=\"1320\" y=\"280\" width=\"30\" height=\"15\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                <text x=\"1360\" y=\"287\" class=\"legend-text\">3x3 Convolution</text>\n                \n                <circle cx=\"1335\" cy=\"310\" r=\"8\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                <text x=\"1360\" y=\"315\" class=\"legend-text\">Element-wise Addition</text>\n                \n                <line x1=\"1320\" y1=\"340\" x2=\"1350\" y2=\"340\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                <text x=\"1360\" y=\"345\" class=\"legend-text\">Bottom-up Flow</text>\n                \n                <line x1=\"1320\" y1=\"365\" x2=\"1350\" y2=\"365\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n                <text x=\"1360\" y=\"370\" class=\"legend-text\">Top-down Flow</text>\n                \n                <line x1=\"1320\" y1=\"390\" x2=\"1350\" y2=\"390\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n                <text x=\"1360\" y=\"395\" class=\"legend-text\">Lateral Connection</text>\n                \n                <line x1=\"1320\" y1=\"415\" x2=\"1350\" y2=\"415\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n                <text x=\"1360\" y=\"420\" class=\"legend-text\">Final Output</text>\n                \n                <text x=\"1320\" y=\"450\" class=\"legend-text\">Tensor Shapes:</text>\n                <text x=\"1320\" y=\"470\" class=\"legend-text\">B = Batch size</text>\n                <text x=\"1320\" y=\"485\" class=\"legend-text\">H,W = Height, Width</text>\n                \n                <!-- Arrow markers -->\n                <defs>\n                    <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                        <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                    </marker>\n                    <marker id=\"arrowhead-red\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                        <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#e74c3c\"/>\n                    </marker>\n                    <marker id=\"arrowhead-orange\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                        <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#f39c12\"/>\n                    </marker>\n                    <marker id=\"arrowhead-green\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                        <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#27ae60\"/>\n                    </marker>\n                    <marker id=\"arrowhead-purple\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                        <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#9b59b6\"/>\n                    </marker>\n                </defs>\n            </svg>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Feature Pyramid Network (FPN)</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .content {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: flex-start;\n        }\n        \n        .diagram {\n            flex: 1;\n            margin-right: 40px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend {\n            width: 300px;\n            background: white;\n            border: 2px solid #34495e;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        \n        .legend-title {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #34495e;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-color {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #7f8c8d;\n            border-radius: 3px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-line {\n            width: 30px;\n            height: 2px;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title\">Feature Pyramid Network (FPN)</div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"diagram\">\n                <svg width=\"1540\" height=\"900\" viewBox=\"0 0 1540 900\">\n                    <!-- Background -->\n                    <rect width=\"1540\" height=\"900\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Bottom-up Backbone Pathway (Left Column) -->\n                    <!-- C5 (1/32) - Top, smallest -->\n                    <rect x=\"80\" y=\"120\" width=\"180\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"165\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">C5 (1/32)</text>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">512 channels</text>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Bx16x16x512</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- C4 (1/16) -->\n                    <rect x=\"60\" y=\"280\" width=\"220\" height=\"140\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">C4 (1/16)</text>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">256 channels</text>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Bx32x32x256</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- C3 (1/8) -->\n                    <rect x=\"40\" y=\"460\" width=\"260\" height=\"160\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">C3 (1/8)</text>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"545\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">128 channels</text>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"565\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Bx64x64x128</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- C2 (1/4) - Bottom, largest -->\n                    <rect x=\"20\" y=\"660\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"735\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">C2 (1/4)</text>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"755\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">64 channels</text>\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"775\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">Bx128x128x64</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Backbone flow arrows -->\n                    <path d=\"M 170 240 L 170 260\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 170 420 L 170 440\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 170 620 L 170 640\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- 1x1 Conv Lateral Connections -->\n                    <!-- C5 to merge point -->\n                    <rect x=\"320\" y=\"165\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"380\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">1x1 conv</text>\n                    <path d=\"M 260 180 L 300\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 440 180 L 480\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- C4 to merge point -->\n                    <rect x=\"320\" y=\"335\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"380\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">1x1 conv</text>\n                    <path d=\"M 280 350 L 300\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 440 350 L 480\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- C3 to merge point -->\n                    <rect x=\"320\" y=\"525\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"380\" y=\"545\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">1x1 conv</text>\n                    <path d=\"M 300 540 L 300\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 440 540 L 480\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- C2 to merge point -->\n                    <rect x=\"320\" y=\"735\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"380\" y=\"755\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">1x1 conv</text>\n                    <path d=\"M 320 750 L 300\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 440 750 L 480\" stroke=\"#3498db\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Element-wise Addition Nodes -->\n                    <circle cx=\"500\" cy=\"180\" r=\"20\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"186\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">+</text>\n                    \n                    <circle cx=\"500\" cy=\"350\" r=\"20\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"356\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">+</text>\n                    \n                    <circle cx=\"500\" cy=\"540\" r=\"20\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"546\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">+</text>\n                    \n                    <circle cx=\"500\" cy=\"750\" r=\"20\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"756\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">+</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- 2x Upsample arrows (top-down) -->\n                    <rect x=\"420\" y=\"240\" width=\"100\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"257\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">2x upsample</text>\n                    <path d=\"M 500 200 L 500 220\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 500 265 L 500 330\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"420\" y=\"430\" width=\"100\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"447\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">2x upsample</text>\n                    <path d=\"M 500 370 L 500 410\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 500 455 L 500 520\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"420\" y=\"640\" width=\"100\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"657\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">2x upsample</text>\n                    <path d=\"M 500 560 L 500 620\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 500 665 L 500 730\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- 3x3 Conv blocks -->\n                    <rect x=\"560\" y=\"165\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"610\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">3x3 conv</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"560\" y=\"335\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"610\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">3x3 conv</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"560\" y=\"525\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"610\" y=\"545\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">3x3 conv</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"560\" y=\"735\" width=\"100\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n                    <text x=\"610\" y=\"755\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">3x3 conv</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Arrows from addition to 3x3 conv -->\n                    <path d=\"M 520 180 L 540\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 520 350 L 540\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 520 540 L 540\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 520 750 L 540\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Top-down Pathway Output Features (Right Column) -->\n                    <!-- P5 -->\n                    <rect x=\"720\" y=\"150\" width=\"160\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#16a085\" stroke=\"#138d75\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">P5</text>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">256-d</text>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">Bx16x16x256</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- P4 -->\n                    <rect x=\"720\" y=\"320\" width=\"160\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#16a085\" stroke=\"#138d75\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"345\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">P4</text>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"365\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">256-d</text>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"380\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">Bx32x32x256</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- P3 -->\n                    <rect x=\"720\" y=\"510\" width=\"160\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#16a085\" stroke=\"#138d75\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"535\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">P3</text>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"555\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">256-d</text>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"570\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">Bx64x64x256</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- P2 -->\n                    <rect x=\"720\" y=\"720\" width=\"160\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#16a085\" stroke=\"#138d75\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"6\"/>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"745\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">P2</text>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"765\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">256-d</text>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"780\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"white\">Bx128x128x256</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Arrows from 3x3 conv to P outputs -->\n                    <path d=\"M 660 180 L 700\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 660 350 L 700\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 660 540 L 700\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 660 750 L 700\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Arrow marker definition -->\n                    <defs>\n                        <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                            <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        </marker>\n                    </defs>\n                    \n                    <!-- Labels for pathways -->\n                    <text x=\"170\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Bottom-up Pathway</text>\n                    <text x=\"800\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Top-down Pathway</text>\n                </svg>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"legend\">\n                <div class=\"legend-title\">Legend</div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #e74c3c;\"></div>\n                    <span>Backbone Features (C2-C5)</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #3498db;\"></div>\n                    <span>1x1 Convolution (Lateral)</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #9b59b6;\"></div>\n                    <span>2x Upsampling</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #f39c12;\"></div>\n                    <span>Element-wise Addition</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #27ae60;\"></div>\n                    <span>3x3 Convolution</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background-color: #16a085;\"></div>\n                    <span>Pyramid Features (P2-P5)</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background-color: #2c3e50;\"></div>\n                    <span>Data Flow</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #7f8c8d;\">\n                    <strong>Tensor Shapes:</strong><br>\n                    B = Batch size<br>\n                    Spatial dims decrease by 2x<br>\n                    All P-levels: 256 channels\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}